the cosby show finished in the top 10 
twice in the ac nielsen co ratings while more people watched 
the color purple than the first part of the kennedys of 
massachusetts miniseries 
nbc won the ratings race for the week ended feb 18 with an 
average of 157 followed by abc with 126 and cbs with 121 
according to figures released tuesday a ratings point represents 
the percentage of the nations 921 million television shows tuned 
into a show 
here are the top 10 shows their networks and ratings the 
cosby show nbc 239 cheers nbc 233 tie movie of 
the week blind faith part 2 nbc 233 a different world 
nbc 219 the cosby show special nbc 216 americas 
funniest home videos abc 212 roseanne abc 205 the 
golden girls nbc 204 empty nest nbc 199 the wonder 
years abc 194 
nbc scored strongly on monday night by using a special airing of 
the cosby show the golden girls dear john and empty 
nest the network claimed a 10 percent gain above its normal 
monday average 
also monday cbs the love boat a valentine voyage was 38th 
in the ratings while abcs broadcast of jewel of the nile was 
41st 
nbc won all the nights of the week except friday against abcs 
lineup and sunday when it offered the death of the incredible 
hulk against cbs broadcast of the theatrical movie the color 
purple and abcs first installment of the kennedys miniseries 
the color purple took 18th place with a 171 rating 
followed by the kennedys tied at 20th with a 158 rating and 
the hulk movie tied for no 24 with a 146 rating 
americas funniest home videos was in 6th place on abc with 
a 212 rating but elvis the midseason show following it 
