1977 to l982 his diplomatic intiatives contributed to unions of 
reformed and congregational churches in many countries 
a native texan mccord was president and professor of theology 
at princeton theological seminary from 1959 until his retirement in 
1983 that year he became chancellor of princetons center for 
theological inquiry which he had founded 
he retired from that post last year 
