the telephone network reached by dialing 18002345ssa is 
staffed from 7 am to 7 pm across the country and allows 
callers to take care of many matters without going into a social 
security office in many cities the tollfree number is the only 
social security number listed in the phone book 
but congressional critics complain people often are unable to 
get through on the tollfree lines and that many dont get full and 
accurate information when they do get through 
