prevented by congress from lifting us sanctions 
he went on to say the steps we are taking are positive and 
added that he feels very strongly that when someone does what you 
are asking you should recognize that fact said hurd 
britain is the largest single foreign investor in south africa 
although several major british corporations and the londonbased 
