giving about 40000 miners two tracts of national park land in 
exchange for the prospectors promise to leave the yanomami reserve 
mucci said only congress could authorize the location of mining 
sites and the type of minerals to be extracted on national forest 
land 
he threatened to bring charges against the ministers of justice 
health interior air force and mines and energy for cosigning the 
decree 
