for every kosher restaurant on todays south miami beach the 
socalled jewish riviera theres a fern bar or a counter 
restaurant featuring cuban or nicaraguan standards 
the jewish population is sharply declining on the famed 
41blocklong stretch spurred by an increase in latin exiles 
modern phenomena such as condominiums marielitos and yuppies and 
that most ancient earthly problem mortality 
when i first came here this building was 99 percent jewish 
