who have decided to take this action are prepared to accept those 
consequences fauntroy said last week 
perhaps but if there really is such a statehood campaign it 
would create a special dilemma for jackson who would have to 
choose between local and national objectives tax disobedience 
might play well in the district of columbia but it could be 
disastrous in any future presidential campaign 
