theoretically 
your doctors fee might have doubled but most likely you are 
getting better health care too youre probably getting more 
pounds of health care for the dollar that is the cost of a pound 
of health care might have dropped 
then we might assume that some of service inflation isnt real 
it isnt an assumption said dunkelberg it is a fact 
