is a problem that questrom readily acknowledged 
obviously in the short term thats a key issue but i think 
were working very aggressively with our vendors to be sure that we 
do get deliveries on schedule he said ninetyeight percent of 
the vendors want federated to be successful theyre working 
towards that aim we all get the same benefit out of being 
successful 
